<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4290613>
    dc:description "Figure 1. (a–f) Torymus lasallei, holotype female. (a), habitus, lateral (inset - detail of ovipositor setation); (b), head, dorsal; (c), head, lateral; (d), antennal clava, arrows indicate micropilosity areas; (e), head, detail of lower face; (f), antenna, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4290613/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4290617>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Torymus lasallei, holotype female (a–c, e–h), paratype female (d). (a), mesosoma, dorsal; (b), mesosoma, lateral; (c), metascutellum and propodeum, dorsal; (d), left hind leg, outer aspect; (e), metasoma, dorsal; (f), right wings, dorsal; (g), part of submarginal, marginal, postmarginal and stigmal vein, dorsal detail; (h), part of marginal, postmarginal and stigmal vein, dorsal detail." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4290617/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4290619>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Torymus lasallei, female. Habitus of female collected in Parque Ecológico El Huixteco (Guerrero State, Mexico) on Quercus castanea from Amphibolips nr hidalgoensis galls (photo by Leticia Valencia)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4290619/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4290621>
    dc:description "Figure 4. (a–c) Torymus texanus, female. (a), habitus, lateral; (b), habitus, dorsal; (c), head, anterior." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4290621/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

